670
00:55:26,940 --> 00:55:30,460
After that was the title
track, "Break Down."

671
00:55:30,460 --> 00:55:36,730
The strong performance stood out
as it showed off masculinity.

672
00:55:36,730 --> 00:55:40,070
He even reached the top
with this song.

673
00:55:59,840 --> 00:56:05,780
